      "text": [
        " اَلرَّجُلِ يُصَلِّي وَ عَلَيْهِ خَاتَمُ حَدِيدٍ قَالَ «لاَ وَ لاَ يَتَخَتَّمُ بِهِ لِأَنَّهُ مِنْ لِبَاسِ أَهْلِ اَلنَّارِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.774 - Ammar al-Sabati narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) regarding a man who prays while wearing an iron ring.\nImam (as) said: \"No, and he should not wear it, for it is the attire of the people of the Fire.\""
        ]
      }
